nodes.text: Inspector-General was a title in the Galactic Empire. Sometime between the years 19 and 1 BBY, Moff Rebu held the position of Inspector-General.

The title of Inspector-General was first mentioned in "The Nemesis Gunship" entry in the in-game databank of the PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 versions of Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II, a LucasArts video game released in 2010.
